name: get_one_set_by_id
description:
This is a sub-function API for tool pokemon_tcg_card_prices.
Tool description: Provides a model of the Pokemon Trading Card Game cards.
Each individual card has a price that is based on recent sales of the card or currently open listings.
API description: Returns information about a single Pokémon TCG set by retrieving data using the set ID.

setid.description: The ID of the Pokémon TCG set for which information is to be retrieved.
